    "9, 10, 11, 12, 13, 14 and Table 16.",
    "The ALBERT model performs best in a single model, with an accuracy of 0.766 and an F1 score of 0.775.",
    "But the ensemble learning model we proposed can make the accuracy reach 0.787, and the F1 score can reach 0.795.",
